title: No traces
description:
This cog lets you toggle a no-traces mode that will autodelete **all** your messages after a certain amount of time.
The command that comes with this cog is
- `notrace [seconds to delete]` to toggle the notrace mode.

[(Check the Source Code)](https://github.com/Bluscream/Discord-Selfbot-Cogs/blob/master/notraces.py)
author: Bluscream#2597
